
Polymorphism ----> one thing can have many form that called Polymorphism.

poly -----> many
morphism -----> form

eg ---->
1) Shape - circle, square, triangle, rectangle, etc
2) water - vapour, ice burg, liquid etc


***** We can achieve Polymorphism using Method Overloading.

4 Rules are applicable
----------------------------
1) Method name should be same
2) Number of parameter should be different
3) Data type of parameter should be different
4) Order of parameter should be different

** In Overloading we not consider return type, we only consider parameter **

